{"tid":1198521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一位老師，喺政總外遇上一名學生","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:22:18.000Z","uid":40368,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9ebfa9d6a07da5da4e47f4ac2d2d5d44836ad3","tid":1198521,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"我係一位老師，尋日遊行到政府總部休息時<br />\n<br />\n巧遇一名中二級既女學生自己一個人企喺到<br />\n<br />\n我：「你一個人既？等緊同學呀？」<br />\n<br />\n佢：「唔係，我自己一個黎。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「你咁大膽，要小心啲播。」<br />\n<br />\n佢：「我準備走架啦，夜返俾呀媽鬧。」<br />\n<br />\n佢唔知地鐵站喺邊，問完我就自己走左去<br />\n<br />\n同行朋友問我使唔使送佢去地鐵站<br />\n<br />\n我話佢一個人有勇氣行出黎，已經唔使擔心佢<br />\n<br />\n而今日啱啱完成左佢既中文科考試，一切順利<br />\n<br />\n一啲考慮緊行唔行出黎、好忙好熱好攰唔出現既「大人」們<br />\n<br />\n你地又仲有咩借口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8e53260c88d0971bc277d27ffc4fc1d86dc413","tid":1198521,"uid":217244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35afd815ccd843888896d51118663dc81f040478","tid":1198521,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf8e53260c88d0971bc277d27ffc4fc1d86dc413","tid":1198521,"uid":217244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"34487a7213b08768d94cdbe8525b7ae1b42d523d","tid":1198521,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ad0d96502afc7a4efab3af646a3abe1555d274","tid":1198521,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e